    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Clearing Blade：为您而来的 Roguelite 冒险！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个充满黑暗的世界遭受着怪物的不断侵袭。随着时间的推移，许多战士和法师要么被敌人打败，要么沦为俘虏。现在，轮到你了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/4502237acbdbcf733fb6c985cd0a2669.poster.avif?t=1734584212\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/4502237acbdbcf733fb6c985cd0a2669.webm?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/4502237acbdbcf733fb6c985cd0a2669.mp4?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗的序幕即将拉开！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抵御敌人的潮水，营救在战场上被俘的同伴。被救出的同伴将给予你力量，帮助你与黑暗势力抗衡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/65fdff6f1e27c252d659492babb31511.poster.avif?t=1734584212\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/65fdff6f1e27c252d659492babb31511.webm?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/65fdff6f1e27c252d659492babb31511.mp4?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与同伴们一起团结力量！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与战士们共同作战，击败敌人，获得惊人的能力。只要团结在一起，就能克服任何挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/dc94002f5c363a58a4698bb0ebf623cc.poster.avif?t=1734584212\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/dc94002f5c363a58a4698bb0ebf623cc.webm?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/dc94002f5c363a58a4698bb0ebf623cc.mp4?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >绝对不要放弃！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Clearing Blade 是一款专为全球热爱 Hack and Slash 和 Roguelite 的玩家设计的挑战性游戏。</i>操作简单，但由于其 Soul-like 特性，需要深思熟虑的战略。来测试你的技能吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/979ea509b7ff751d16bf415beb1f0d15.poster.avif?t=1734584212\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/979ea509b7ff751d16bf415beb1f0d15.webm?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/979ea509b7ff751d16bf415beb1f0d15.mp4?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数字的力量！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果力量不足，驻地的居民和同伴们随时准备帮助你。只需记住，要获得他们的支持，你需要准备一些<i>小奖励</i>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/9db256952edb232664ea6c3801316d70.poster.avif?t=1734584212\" width=690 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/9db256952edb232664ea6c3801316d70.webm?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/9db256952edb232664ea6c3801316d70.mp4?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好响应英雄的召唤吗？</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跳入 Clearing Blade 的动作中，刻下英雄的传奇。战场在等待你的命令！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在早期访问中，您可以享受以下内容：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手感极佳的以动作为中心的 Roguelite Hack and Slash</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三种不同技能的角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 种以上的多样敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 种强大而独特的 Boss</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 种个性鲜明的地图</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进度保存的 Roguelite 机制</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在正式版本中，我们将通过基于社区反馈的持续更新来增强稳定性和游戏体验。您的参与和意见将大大促进我们游戏的发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/312af0f255636ca45569f5fe97bfe3c1.poster.avif?t=1734584212\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/312af0f255636ca45569f5fe97bfe3c1.webm?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065500/extras/312af0f255636ca45569f5fe97bfe3c1.mp4?t=1734584212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
